title: 303: My White Whale

description:
On this weeks episode, Dr. Cox's freaks out when Jack gets sick eventually going to all out war with the best pediatrician in the hospital. In the real world, Zach and Donald remember Roscoe, the best dog in the world. Joelle talks about her birthday celebration, and Donald's stunt double remembers the time monkeys came to visit the set.
